column5: I'd like to wish all of my family and friends the best year for 2015. Only 16 hours to go roughly so make the best of it.  Have a happy, safe and healthy year. I don't do prosperous anymore because I figure that if you have healthy and happy, you already have everything.  Bless you all.
Happy new Years to you as well Roy!!!!And all the best to everyone in 2015!!  .
Same to you Roy & OFC, all the best in the new year.
A heartfelt thanks, guys,

Happy New Year to you too Big Guy !!! 2014 has been an amazing year for me personally. Nat and I were married on July 12th, and I am living a happiness I never knew existed. I got out locally 4-5 times this year for walleye, but nothing reportable. It's enough to keep me hooked  Happy New year to all of you too. Health and happiness to all.
Happy New Year Roy
Happy New Year and the best of health to everyone.
Happy New Year , Roy ! And to all the folks at OFC !
All the best to everyone and their families in 2015.
Right back at you Roy and J.  Looking forward to bunking with you two in July 2015.   Happy New Year!!!!!
Happy New Year Roy, J and all at OFC!
Happy new year me brudder. A very quite night, and now  up to start the year fishing.  Good health to you and J and all the kiddies.
Happy New Year all.  Hope a PB in everyone's boat this year
I'm wishing every one here a healthy & happy New Year!
Happy New Year to you Roy and J  Best Fishes to everyone at OFC, I may not be around much these days, but you guys are never far from my thoughts.  Here's to a great 2015!  Maureen
I don't do prosperous anymore because I figure that if you have healthy and happy, you already have everything.  Yes indeedy doo! Very well put!! and a good one to you!
X2

Great on you buddy Happy New Year

I'd like to wish all of my family and friends the best year for 2015. Only 16 hours to go roughly so make the best of it.  Have a happy, safe and healthy year. I don't do prosperous anymore because I figure that if you have healthy and happy, you already have everything.  Bless you all. Happy New Year to you my Friend

Happy New Year to you big guy from the both of us as well to all the good people here at OFC.  This past year has been challenging for many of us members here. We almost lost our sister and if there is such a thing as a miracle I was witness to one. She was given last rights in April and we just spoke with her today, she had just come back from a walk with the dogs at the cottage. I told her she owes me for a new black suit I never needed to use.
